ARMS 💀🥵 Bi’s, Tri’s, & Forearms.. (it’s just the pump.. my arms aren’t as big as they may appear fam) lol CLOCK IN! It’s rough ⚠️ 

1. EZ Bar Finger Lifts - 4x10 - keep your arms straight (not bent) move only your fingers.. this is a forearm exercise.. try not to engage anything else

2. EZ Bar Hammer Curls - Hold for 10 seconds & then do 10 💀🥵

3. EZ Bar Reverse Finger Lifts - 4x10 - pause at the top (grab light weight) maybe 30lbs 

4. EZ Bar Lying Skull Crushers - 4x12 - squeeze at the top & move slow (TRI’S) 

5. EZ Bar Curls - 4x12 - don’t go too heavy here, focus on form first fam 

6. Kneeling Tricep Exts - 4x12 - keep a tight core for balance and work on perfect technique 

Tap in fam.. from me to you 🫶🏾🤝.
